&lt;/code&gt;&lt;/pre&gt;

&lt;/div&gt;



&lt;p&gt;The first time you run this, it will download the model weights from Hugging Face. Subsequent runs load from cache in seconds.&lt;/p&gt;




&lt;h2&gt;


Your First Text-to-Mask Prediction
&lt;/h2&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Let's verify everything works with a single image:&lt;br&gt;
&lt;/p&gt;

